## 8. Appendix

### Glossary

| Term | Definition |
| --- | --- |
| QuickPick | VS Code native dropdown UI component for item selection |
| Embedding Model | ONNX neural network that converts text into 384-dimensional vectors |
| ModelManager | Backend component handling model lifecycle |
| ModelRegistry | JSON file tracking downloaded models and active selection |
| HuggingFace | Model hosting platform |
| ONNX | Open Neural Network Exchange — portable model format |
| Codicon | VS Code’s built-in icon font |
| MCP | Model Context Protocol |

### HTTP API Quick Reference

| Method | Path | Request Body | Success Response |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| GET | /api/models/list | — | { models: [{name, display\_name, size\_mb, languages, downloaded, active}] } |
| GET | /api/models/status | — | { active\_model, model\_path, dimensions } |
| POST | /api/models/download | { model\_name } | { success: true, status: “downloading” } |
| POST | /api/models/switch | { model\_name } | { success: true, active\_model } |